summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department, accepting an easement for fire hydrant purposes and eight easements for watermain purposes over portions of: Jardin El Norte; Section 2, Township 23 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; Plat of Lake Dell; Loch-Gilvra Addition; Section 28, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; Section 36, Township 26 North, Range 3 East, W.M.; Cedar Park No. 2; Section 34, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; Section 31, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M. and H.E. Orr Park Division No. 7 all in King County, Washington (Private Contracts).
